@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

component "RoomService" as RoomSvc
component "MatchService" as MatchSvc
component "TournamentService" as TourSvc
component "ChatService" as Chat
component "ProposalService" as ProposalSvc

component "DomainEventService" as Events
database "domain_event_log" as EventLog
component "Analytics Projector" as Projector
database "analytics tables / materialized views" as AnalyticsDB
component "Future Stats API" as StatsAPI
actor "User / Admin" as User

RoomSvc --> Events : room events
MatchSvc --> Events : match events
TourSvc --> Events : tournament events
Chat --> Events : chat events
ProposalSvc --> Events : proposal events

Events --> EventLog
Events --> Projector : stream / polling

Projector --> AnalyticsDB : aggregated stats
StatsAPI --> AnalyticsDB
User --> StatsAPI

note right of Projector
Later responsibilities:
- player progression metrics
- room activity summaries
- win/loss aggregates
- reconnect/abandonment rates
- cognitive game performance trends
end note

note right of EventLog
Keep raw events as the durable source
for replayable business analytics.
end note
@enduml
